Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.45,0:00:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything \Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.57,0:00:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.42,0:00:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything this \Nworld has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now everyone is in search of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.86,0:00:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered \Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:26.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:30.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,jitto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.52,0:00:30.50,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Daybreak hasn’t come yet and I can’t wait
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.52,0:00:34.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yoake ga osokute jirettai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.77,0:00:34.75,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.77,0:00:40.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:40.05,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly the flag, Break of Romance Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:45.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,hata wo ageyou Break of Romance Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:45.56,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make waves, jump from your sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:50.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,namikaze tateyou suriipu kara no janpusutaato
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:50.85,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to go to the unbelievable world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:55.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,arienai sekai wo iku nara
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:00:55.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,your toughness, that’s what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:01:00.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kimi no tafunesu sore ga hitsuyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:00.07,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Being brazen, is it a crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:02.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,medachisugi sorette tsumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.93,0:01:02.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanted->means Winner:D
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.93,0:01:05.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shimeitehai->tsumari Winner
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.93,0:01:05.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Freedom is our only rule
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.93,0:01:11.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,jiyuu dakega ore tachi no ruuru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.48,0:01:11.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not our way to worry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.48,0:01:16.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinpai nante dokofuku kaze--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.94,0:01:16.92,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,At any cost, One Piece, I’ll be the first
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.94,0:01:19.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ttai one piece ichibannori
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.48,0:01:19.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,My dreaming heart is huge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.48,0:01:23.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume miru kokoro wa choo dekai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.53,0:01:23.51,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s important not to wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.53,0:01:27.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,samenai koto ga daiji--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:27.81,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:30.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:30.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Daybreak hasn’t come yet and I can’t wait
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:34.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yoake ga osokute jirettai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:34.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:39.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:39.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We...made it this far
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:45.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa...koko made kitaze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:45.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We go...to where the dream is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:48.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa iku...yume no arika e
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:48.74,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We won’t left anyone behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:53.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dare mo oitekanaize--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:53.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going forward, that’s our pledge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:56.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nshin aru nomi sore ga chikai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.48,0:01:56.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the day that the dream began
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.48,0:02:00.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume ga hajimatta ano hi kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:00.55,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,the future that I’m \Naiming at hasn’t changed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:04.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,mezasu mirai wa onaji--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.70,0:02:04.68,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.70,0:02:07.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:07.30,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun of my heart will never set
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:11.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kokoro no taiyou shizumanai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.58,0:02:11.56,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.58,0:02:15.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:15.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:19.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.71,0:02:19.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.71,0:02:27.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.30,0:02:36.30,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.73,0:02:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, the second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.32,0:02:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,except for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:03:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many pirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.33,0:03:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.29,0:03:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a boy whose body turned to rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.66,0:03:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.77,0:03:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After surviving a fierce battle at the Fish-Man Island,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Straw Hats finally entered the New World,--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.41,0:03:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the harshest sea ruled by the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.63,0:03:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After receiving an emergency signal, they landed on Punk Hazard Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.66,0:03:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a strange island divided into two parts; the Burning Lands and the Ice Lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let them escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.43,0:03:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?! It's like a thin film...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.17,0:03:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shambles!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.23,0:04:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Everybody, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.46,0:04:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do a roll call!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.72,0:04:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Chopper!\N--Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.40,0:04:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Franky!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.03,0:04:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.68,0:04:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.08,0:04:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Nami... aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.51,0:04:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.80,0:04:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid pirate, don't push your luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.51,0:04:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ate the Op-Op Fruit and you're the Modification Man, I believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.56,0:04:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of his sword's reach!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.79,0:04:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are in my way! Get out of the circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.40,0:04:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The circle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While you're in the circle he created,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're like a patient on an operating table!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.00,0:04:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is his operating room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.84,0:05:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has total control over it and can manipulate anything as he pleases!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the Surgeon of Death!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.88,0:05:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it, Tashigi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Haki is not strong enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.38,0:05:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Collision! Law vs. Vice Admiral Smoker!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.18,0:05:50.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE LABORATORY - IN FRONT OF THE MAIN ENTRANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.21,0:06:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Captain-chan got cut in half!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.71,0:06:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, you're alive, aren't you?!\N--Tashigi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.40,0:06:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dishonorable! I got sliced but I'm still breathing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just kill me, Trafalgar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.23,0:07:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You talk like a master swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you something, Navy soldier girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.04,0:07:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The weak can't even pick their way to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.79,0:07:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't reach me with that sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.70,0:07:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can chop you more if you liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you! Stop insulting our Captain-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.67,0:07:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain-chan, don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.37,0:07:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll riddle that fool with bullets!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.97,0:07:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bullets?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did the bullets get here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did the bullets that we shot go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the bullets you shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.44,0:08:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I switched them with the snow falling over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.45,0:08:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he invincible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.73,0:08:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get down! He's gonna cut everything again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.76,0:08:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can stop his sword attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.73,0:08:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard! Captain-chan, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.78,0:08:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.47,0:08:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smo-yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.07,0:08:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Surgeon of Death--Trafalgar Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.22,0:08:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.73,0:08:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop messing with the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.01,0:09:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel an unpleasant energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have Sea Prism Stone on the tip of your jitte, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.51,0:09:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! The recoil made the sword cut the artwork!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.22,0:09:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship's gonna fall onto us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's run! He doesn't want us to be here anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.52,0:09:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if you're a Warlord or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.13,0:09:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just get out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.33,0:09:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Admiral Smoker!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.87,0:09:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain-chan, let's get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.21,0:09:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--But...\N--He's no match for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.88,0:10:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,White Blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.01,0:10:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! Get out of the circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They were strong... Too strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.31,0:10:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy and his crew...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! They took Boss Brownbeard with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We got to help the Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.47,0:10:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're cold-blooded pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.35,0:10:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what they're gonna do to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss Brownbeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.03,0:10:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to let the Master know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow me, those of you who can stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.53,0:11:01.29,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,THE ICE LANDS - LUFFY'S GROUP
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.31,0:11:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard a huge noise. Was it Sanji and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.49,0:11:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Alliga-taur!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't know what happened to my crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.22,0:11:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I won't tell you anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.91,0:11:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. Then run faster! To the building that Brook saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta save Nami and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.30,0:11:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How humiliating to lose to such a squirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.65,0:11:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You robbed my people so cruelly of all they had, you cheap muggers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to give us a bad name!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys attacked us first!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.14,0:11:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're showing no sign of remorse, alligator guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook, I know you don't feel cold because you don't have flesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.34,0:11:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why did you steal the coat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.83,0:11:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I felt like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.13,0:11:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy to see you all again so I wanted to share in your feeling cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.50,0:12:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad that Nami and the others were abducted in those clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope they don't get frostbite and lose their limbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, Robin! Don't share those gruesome concerns!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.77,0:12:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.91,0:12:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Law and Smoker are in a big battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the plan was just to make them go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.17,0:12:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But those escaped pirates took the kids in the Biscuit Room with them
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.39,0:12:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and ran into Law and the others at the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.87,0:12:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the Navy saw the children?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.27,0:12:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I feared the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.34,0:12:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now they know something is going on on this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.27,0:12:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we kill Smoker,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:12:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Navy will become aware that something is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.85,0:13:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.29,0:13:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just got back - what are you doing now, Monet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.55,0:13:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should have paid better attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.53,0:13:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I forgot to mention.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vegapunk's dragon and
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.32,0:13:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brownbeard's Centaur Patrol Unit have been defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.49,0:13:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.96,0:13:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means those pirates you kidnapped along with
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,their ship had other crew members
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.71,0:13:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they were in the Burning Lands already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.34,0:13:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They made it across the lake and they'll be here in a matter of minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were so strong. Now look.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.64,0:13:43.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE STRAW HATS ARE BACK
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.11,0:13:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it was them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.77,0:13:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.07,0:13:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you have heard about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.59,0:13:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're an unforgivable archenemy not just for the Navy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but for the World Government too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.25,0:13:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The World Government, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.08,0:14:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they're so notorious, maybe it's good for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it's the Straw Hats or Smoker,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.98,0:14:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can get rid of all those troublemakers who are learning what's
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.56,0:14:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,going on on this island at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.86,0:14:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Master, even if they're a group of misfits,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.26,0:14:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if we kill all the G-5 soldiers,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.83,0:14:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Navy would be on the alert, wouldn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.23,0:14:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we can just suppress things that are going to
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.71,0:14:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,happen on the island from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.92,0:14:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Call Joker.\N--Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.60,0:15:06.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A MOUNTAIN BEHIND THE LABORATORY SANJI'S GROUP
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it out from the backdoor but what should we do now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.03,0:15:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with this strange transformation going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.62,0:15:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we have to keep running for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.57,0:15:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?! It's super confusing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.55,0:15:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Bros!\N--W-We're gonna freeze to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.56,0:15:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deadly cold? I don't give a damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The samurai and the brats? I don't give a damn anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.04,0:15:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there a camera somewhere?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.76,0:15:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna take a picture before we return to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.43,0:15:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you gonna take a picture of?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.14,0:15:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And stop having nosebleeds in my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.12,0:15:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is more important, Nami! Don't button up my aloha shirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.93,0:15:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's cold but hang on a little bit longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.42,0:15:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Spiral Bro is being kind! It's too creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.90,0:15:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened? Did you get your bodies switched?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.87,0:16:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.59,0:16:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.72,0:16:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being treated very differently from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.21,0:16:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know humans felt this cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.26,0:16:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bros, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.43,0:16:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it... I-I can't even move...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.78,0:16:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Me too!\N--I'm freezing too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.21,0:16:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! We shouldn't have taken them with us when
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we didn't know where to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.19,0:16:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel cold at all with this body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.38,0:17:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pieces of the ship are falling like leaves off a tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Smo-yan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.88,0:17:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain-chan, how is your body? Did they stick together?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.57,0:17:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, your right hand is my left foot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.19,0:17:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My hands! Whose feet are these?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.11,0:17:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! We're in big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.27,0:17:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We lost our means of communication and the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the Warlords were on our side! That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.40,0:17:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey hey, Captain-chan, don't try to move! Stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.55,0:17:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tashigi, keep this in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates will always be pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates will be pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.35,0:18:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one, not even pirates or Government allies,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is allowed to be here on this island, Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means you people are not allowed, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law, why are you here on Punk Hazard?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.43,0:18:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never understood why you joined the Warlords in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.74,0:19:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.41,0:19:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What we need to do now is to achieve higher status.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.27,0:19:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates all over the world have started to pay respect
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.08,0:19:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to the Straw Hats because of the incident at Enies Lobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.43,0:19:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.02,0:19:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put all my pride on the line and kick their asses in the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.84,0:19:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it's the Straw Hats...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or the Warlord who serves for the World Government - Trafalgar Law,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:20:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,pirates will be pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.66,0:20:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never trusted you Warlords.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.33,0:20:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that's the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.28,0:20:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.71,0:21:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.69,0:21:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's behind this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.76,0:21:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you up to on this island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.37,0:21:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you answer first?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.32,0:21:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you all up to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.05,0:21:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are things that you can't see unless you change your standing, Smoker!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.47,0:22:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scalpel!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.31,0:22:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.51,0:22:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have to tell you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.72,0:23:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoker collapses after his heart is stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.78,0:23:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Law looking down coldly before them,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.80,0:23:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the rage of Tashigi and the G-5 reaches\N its peak and they attempt an attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.75,0:23:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Luffy suddenly appears!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.70,0:23:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The meeting between the two, \Nwho share a deep bond from the great war,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.06,0:23:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,causes the situation to drastically change!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.73,0:23:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.06,0:23:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Meeting Again After Two Years!\NLuffy and Law!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.48,0:23:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
